content: this square was inspired by the quatrefoil rosette windows found in gothic architecture it will be the week 9 square for the block-a-week with julieanny crochet along i am so pleased to have the opportunity to submit a square for this amazing cal i sincerely hope you enjoy please note this pattern is intermediate to advanced special thanks to the following ravelry members for testing this square hrdnglynne madaboutpooh aschmidtalso justjilly2 and wuzzel i appreciate all of your help and support please visit my ravelry group for more free patterns https //www ravelry com/groups/this-little-hook-of-mine-designs
